title: Effective Project Management: Traditional, Agile, Extreme, 7th e
description:
2013 | ISBN: 1118729161 | English | 768 pages | PDF | 10 MB

The popular guide to the project management body of knowledge, now fully updated

Now in its seventh edition, this comprehensive guide to project management has long been considered the standard for both professionals and academics. 

With more than 32,000 copies sold in the last three editions, it has now been fully updated to cover the new PMBOK 5. 

Well-known expert Robert Wysocki has added more than 100 pages of new content based on instructor feedback, enhancing the coverage of best-of-breed methods and tools for ensuring project management success.
